# AWS Bastion Host Project

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates how to securely access an EC2 instance located in a private subnet using a Bastion Host deployed in a public subnet within the same AWS VPC.

## Architecture

Internet → Bastion Host (Public Subnet) → Private EC2 Instance (Private Subnet)

### Key Components

* Amazon VPC
* Public Subnet
* Private Subnet
* Internet Gateway
* Route Tables
* Security Groups
* EC2 Instances
* SSH Connectivity

